{"type":"message","id":"08ec9ac3","parentId":"f35ef219","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:59:05.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我将创建一个视觉演示来展示多Agent协作。让我使用canvas工具来创建一个可视化界面，然后创建两个子Agent分别处理时钟和计数器功能。\n\n首先，让我创建一个HTML页面来显示这两个Agent的状态："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_J4TZEFhDFRRurPXVV2jmZv4k","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"multi_agent_demo.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>多Agent协作演示</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        \n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .header h1 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n        \n        .header p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        \n        .agents-container {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(500px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            padding: 40px;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-card {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 3px solid transparent;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        \n        .agent-card.clock-agent {\n            border-color: #3b82f6;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-card.counter-agent {\n            border-color: #10b981;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-header {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            padding-bottom: 15px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-icon {\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 60px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-right: 20px;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: white;\n        }\n        \n        .clock-agent .agent-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8);\n        }\n        \n        .counter-agent .agent-icon {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #047857);\n        }\n        \n        .agent-info h2 {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            color: #1e293b;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-info p {\n            color: #64748b;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-status {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .status-label {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        \n        .status-value {\n            font-size: 3.5rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            min-height: 80px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        \n        .clock-agent .status-value {\n            color: #3b82f6;\n            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n        }\n        \n        .counter-agent .status-value {\n            color: #10b981;\n        }\n        \n        .progress-container {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .progress-bar {\n            height: 10px;\n            background: #e2e8f0;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        .progress-fill {\n            height: 100%;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: width 0.5s ease;\n        }\n        \n        .clock-agent .progress-fill {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #60a5fa);\n        }\n        \n        .counter-agent .progress-fill {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981, #34d399);\n        }\n        \n        .progress-text {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n        }\n        \n        .update-info {\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            padding-top: 15px;\n            border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n        \n        .last-update {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n        \n        .update-dot {\n            width: 8px;\n            height: 8px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n        \n        .clock-agent .update-dot {\n            background: #3b82f6;\n        }\n        \n        .counter-agent .update-dot {\n            background: #10b981;\n        }\n        \n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { opacity: 1; }\n            50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n            100% { opacity: 1; }\n        }\n        \n        .collaboration-visual {\n            padding: 30px;\n            background: #f8fafc;\n            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .collaboration-title {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: #1e293b;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        \n        .agent-connections {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n        \n        .connection-line {\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #10b981);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        \n        .connection-line::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            width: 12px;\n            height: 12px;\n            background: #8b5cf6;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            top: 50%;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n            animation: moveData 2s infinite linear;\n        }\n        \n        @keyframes moveData {\n            0% { left: 0%; }\n            100% { left: 100%; }\n        }\n        \n        .connection-label {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: #64748b;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .agents-container {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n                padding: 20px;\n            }\n            \n            .header h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n            \n            .status-value {\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1>多Agent协作演示</h1>\n            <p>实时时钟Agent + 计数器Agent协同工作，每2秒同步更新状态</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"agents-container\">\n            <div class=\"agent-card clock-agent\">\n                <div class=\"agent-header\">\n                    <div class=\"agent-icon\">🕐</div>\n                    <div class=\"agent-info\">\n                        <h2>实时时钟Agent</h2>\n                        <p>持续显示当前精确时间</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"agent-status\">\n                    <div class=\"status-label\">当前时间</div>\n                    <div class=\"status-value\" id=\"clock-display\">--:--:--</div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"progress-container\">\n                        <div class=\"progress-bar\">\n                            <div class=\"progress-fill\" id=\"clock-progress\" style=\"width: 0%\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"progress-text\">\n                            <span>上次更新</span>\n                            <span id=\"clock-next-update\">2秒后</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"update-info\">\n                    <div class=\"last-update\">\n                        <div class=\"update-dot\"></div>\n                        <span>状态: <span id=\"clock-status\">运行中</span></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span>更新间隔: 2秒</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"agent-card counter-agent\">\n                <div class=\"agent-header\">\n                    <div class=\"agent-icon\">🔢</div>\n                    <div class=\"agent-info\">\n                        <h2>计数器Agent</h2>\n                        <p>从1到5循环计数</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"agent-status\">\n                    <div class=\"status-label\">当前计数</div>\n                    <div class=\"status-value\" id=\"counter-display\">0</div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"progress-container\">\n                        <div class=\"progress-bar\">\n                            <div class=\"progress-fill\" id=\"counter-progress\" style=\"width: 0%\"></div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"progress-text\">\n                            <span>进度</span>\n                            <span id=\"counter-progress-text\">0/5</span>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"update-info\">\n                    <div class=\"last-update\">\n                        <div class=\"update-dot\"></div>\n                        <span>状态: <span id=\"counter-status\">运行中</span></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <span>更新间隔: 2秒</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"collaboration-visual\">\n            <div class=\"collaboration-title\">Agent协作可视化</div>\n            <div class=\"agent-connections\">\n                <div class=\"agent-mini-card clock-agent\">\n                    <div class=\"agent-icon\">🕐</div>\n                    <div>时钟Agent</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"connection-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"connection-label\">数据同步</div>\n                <div class=\"connection-line\"></div>\n                <div class=\"agent-mini-card counter-agent\">\n                    <div class=\"agent-icon\">🔢</div>\n                    <div>计数器Agent</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem;\">\n                两个Agent独立运行但同步更新，每2秒通过主Agent协调状态更新\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // 时钟Agent功能\n        class ClockAgent {\n            constructor() {\n                this.updateInterval = 2000; // 2秒\n                this.lastUpdate = null;\n                this.nextUpdate = null;\n                this.isRunning = true;\n                this.updateCount = 0;\n            }\n            \n            getCurrentTime() {\n                const now = new Date();\n                const hours = now.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0');\n                const minutes = now.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');\n                const seconds = now.getSeconds().toString().padStart(2, '0');\n                const milliseconds = now.getMilliseconds().toString().padStart(3, '0');\n                return `${hours}:${minutes}:${seconds}.${milliseconds}`;\n            }\n            \n            update() {\n                this.lastUpdate = new Date();\n                this.nextUpdate = new Date(this.lastUpdate.getTime() + this.updateInterval);\n                this.updateCount++;\n                \n                return {\n                    time: this.getCurrentTime(),\n                    lastUpdate: this.lastUpdate.toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN'),\n                    nextUpdate: this.nextUpdate.toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN'),\n                    updateCount: this.updateCount,\n                    status: this.isRunning ? '运行中' : '已停止'\n                };\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 计数器Agent功能\n        class CounterAgent {\n            constructor() {\n                this.updateInterval = 2000; // 2秒\n                this.currentCount = 0;\n                this.maxCount = 5;\n                this.isRunning = true;\n                this.updateCount = 0;\n                this.direction = 1; // 1表示递增，-1表示递减\n            }\n            \n            update() {\n                this.updateCount++;\n                \n                // 更新计数\n                this.currentCount += this.direction;\n                \n                // 检查边界\n                if (this.currentCount >= this.maxCount) {\n                    this.currentCount = this.maxCount;\n                    this.direction = -1; // 开始递减\n                } else if (this.currentCount <= 1) {\n                    this.currentCount = 1;\n                    this.direction = 1; // 开始递增\n                }\n                \n                const progress = ((this.currentCount - 1) / (this.maxCount - 1)) * 100;\n                \n                return {\n                    count: this.currentCount,\n                    progress: progress,\n                    progressText: `${this.currentCount}/${this.maxCount}`,\n                    updateCount: this.updateCount,\n                    status: this.isRunning ? '运行中' : '已停止',\n                    direction: this.direction > 0 ? '递增' : '递减'\n                };\n            }\n        }\n        \n        // 初始化Agent\n        const clockAgent = new ClockAgent();\n        const counterAgent = new CounterAgent();\n        \n        // 更新显示的函数\n        function updateDisplay() {\n            // 更新时钟\n            const clockData = clockAgent.update();\n            document.getElementById('clock-display').textContent = clockData.time;\n            document.getElementById('clock-status').textContent = clockData.status;\n            document.getElementById('clock-next-update').textContent = `下次更新: ${clockData.nextUpdate}`;\n            \n            // 更新进度条\n            const now = new Date();\n            const timeSinceUpdate = now - clockAgent.lastUpdate;\n            const progressPercent = (timeSinceUpdate / clockAgent.updateInterval) * 100;\n            document.getElementById('clock-progress').style.width = `${Math.min(progressPercent, 100)}%`;\n            \n            // 更新计数器\n            const counterData = counterAgent.update();\n            document.getElementById('counter-display').textContent = counterData.count;\n            document.getElementById('counter-status').textContent = counterData.status;\n            document.getElementById('counter-progress-text').textContent = counterData.progressText;\n            document.getElementById('counter-progress').style.width = `${counterData.progress}%`;\n            \n            // 添加视觉反馈\n            document.getElementById('clock-display').style.transform = 'scale(1.05)';\n            document.getElementById('counter-display').style.transform = 'scale(1.05)';\n            \n            setTimeout(() => {\n                document.getElementById('clock-display').style.transform = 'scale(1)';\n                document.getElementById('counter-display').style.transform = 'scale(1)';\n            }, 200);\n            \n            // 记录更新\n            console.log(`更新 #${clockData.updateCount}: 时钟=${clockData.time}, 计数器=${counterData.count}`);\n        }\n        \n        // 初始更新\n        updateDisplay();\n        \n        // 设置定时器，每2秒更新一次\n        setInterval(updateDisplay, 2000);\n        \n        // 添加一些样式到mini卡片\n        const style = document.createElement('style');\n        style.textContent = `\n            .agent-mini-card {\n                display: flex;\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n                padding: 15px;\n                background: white;\n                border-radius: 10px;\n                box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n                min-width: 100px;\n            }\n            \n            .agent-mini-card .agent-icon {\n                width: 40px;\n                height: 40px;\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n                margin-right: 0;\n                margin-bottom: 10px;\n            }\n            \n            .agent-mini-card div:last-child {\n                font-weight: 600;\n                color: #1e293b;\n            }\n        `;\n        document.head.appendChild(style);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":8982,"output":3934,"cacheRead":640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772726191252}}
